    This object indicates the serial number of the serial numbered object used in the instance.

    Use the newSerialNumberMapping static factory method(s), not the SerialNumberMapping constructor, to construct instances of this class. Instances must be constructed using the static factory(s), in order to ensure proper initialization of the instance.
